properties.name: Parking
properties.desc: Park here at the roundabout circle in McLeay Park.  Head off south on the trail under the Thurman Street Bridge.

properties.name: Crossing Cornell Road
properties.desc: Head across Cornell Road and start up the ascent to the top and Pittock Mansion on the Wildwood Trail.

properties.name: Pittock Mansion
properties.desc: Enjoy the views on the loop path on the grounds around Pittock Mansion and if it is open make sure to go inside.  This has been the site of several famous movies.  You will have great views of Portland.  Make sure to keep an eye out for birds of prey circling the sky above.

properties.name: Lower Macleay Park to Pittock Mansion
